channel.description:
[center] [ul][URL=http://img687.imageshack.us/i/ejdkp1.png/][IMG]http://img687.imageshack.us/img687/7106/ejdkp1.png[/img][/URL][/center]
[b][size=10pt]IF YOUR GOING TO USE THIS SOURCE GIVE ME SOME FEEDBACK, THANKS.[/size][/b]
[size=10pt][u][b]Downloads[/b][/u][/size] [s]50[/s] [s]100[/s] [s]150[/s] [s]200[/s] [s]250[/s] [s]300[/s] 500 1000
Ok basically i'm releasing this for some reasons:
Our Staff isn't active The Server wasn't going anywhere People who I relied on failed me Staff trying to take my money Helping my friend and some other stuff.
I've learnt so much from this Project and yet I didn't even finish it.
Hope you like it guys, something decent to be added, have fun useing it, I didn't release it as it wasn't finished so I hope you guys finish it and make a better job on it then i did :). It has a small anti-leech, a failed "comment". I couldn't care less if you flamed, flamers have no life but "troll" 24/7.
All teleports have been handled through the Mystery guy, [b]like[/b] Impact v2.
This Server is pretty Stable and most NPC's have been cleaned out.
Links:
Source: http://uppit.com/l1hw11ttyk3c/ChronicleX.rar
Client: http://uppit.com/z5rakvnjp6kf/ChronicleX_Client.rar
[u][b]What we've been working on[/b][/u]
We strive to make our players as happy as possible by achieveing the following;
An active Community A stable server Economy Vps Hosted Even more Minigames Tonnes of Bosses/Monsters to battle against! Donating rights Perfect Combat Sensational Pking Amazing PvN & PvP Every Skill, Combat and none working! Double Xp Weekends! Webclient playable
[u][b]What we want to achieve;[/b][/u] #A decent player rate #An active Economy #An all-round fun Server to play #A gripping Server, not a 5 minute Server #A new Server for people to explore!
[u][b]Npc progess[/b][/u] Npc agression Npc following (ONLY MINIGAME FOLLOWING ATM) Clipped Npcs Npc Path Finding Npc Grinding Updated Npc Dialogue (more efficent)
[u][b]What's to come?[/b][/u]
Client adjustable, Fullscreen or small Hd objects
These will be in the late Development^.
Green = Complete Yellow = In the making Red = Yet to complete
-Minigames- [list] [li]Recipe For Disaster[/li] [li]Duel Arena[/li] [list] [li]Castle Wars[/li] [li]Barrows[/li] [list] [li]Fight Caves/Fight Pits[/li] [li]Ancient monsters[/li] [li]Warriors Guild (70% done)[/li][/list] [li]PestControl[/li] [li]Godwars[/li][/list]
More will be coming soon after we've finished the above list.
[u][b]Skilling Base;[/b][/u]
Some skills (In the process of adding them)
Herblore - Vial filling uses Event Manager, 100% perfect potion mixing Runecrafting - 100% Talisman locating, perfect double mulitpler formula for each altar, when Runecrafting level is higher. Thieveing - Correct timing, animations and required level Cooking - Every fish type cookable, correct animations and required level (nothing special) Woodcutting - Recently added Mining - Recently added Fishing - Recently added Fletching - Recently added Crafting - Recently added
